Hi Team,

We are preparing a new OpenShift cluster build and need assistance with creating the required DNS records.

Could you please create the following records within the subnet 172.18.80.x (or the appropriate cluster subnet)?

- API record: api.<cluster-name>.<domain>
- API internal record: api-int.<cluster-name>.<domain>
- Wildcard apps record: *.apps.<cluster-name>.<domain>

Please let us know if any additional information is required.

Thank you,
